item.title: CVE-2021-25316|2024-09-17T03:32:49.137Z -- suse -- suse%20linux%20enterprise%20server%2012-sp5
item.description: A Insecure Temporary File vulnerability in s390-tools of SUSE Linux Enterprise Server 12-SP5, SUSE Linux Enterprise Server 15-SP2 allows local attackers to prevent VM live migrations This issue affects: SUSE Linux Enterprise Server 12-SP5 s390-tools versions prior to 2.1.0-18.29.1. SUSE Linux Enterprise Server 15-SP2 s390-tools versions prior to 2.11.0-9.20.1.
